g.title: EleanorRank4Convo4 begins.
g.text: EleanorRank4Convo4 begins.

g.title: j1268377856
g.text: Were you and Lettie ever friends?

g.title: j2020002043
g.text: This is a pretty close knit group. Have any of you ever dated anyone else in the Hex?

g.title: j2752281512
g.text: How would you take it if Arthur got involved with someone romantically?

g.title: j721522405
g.text: Oh Gods, yeah. We were thick as thieves for a while.

g.title: j708487319
g.text: That's a little personal, mate, but I'll allow it. You've been with us a while. You deserve to know the lay of the land.

g.title: j2948821663
g.text: Someone not a million miles away, you mean?

g.title: j1114436743
g.text: That was before Entrati, of course.

g.title: j2812413792
g.text: Apart from Arthur and Aoi dating? No. Not that I know about, anyway... and I WOULD know.

g.title: j2825035040
g.text: Don't answer that.

g.title: j3829278627
g.text: Now she acts like I’m a different person. Convenient for her. If I’m not really Eleanor then she can be as hurtful towards me as she wants, because she’s not hurting the person she knew. I think it’s cowardly.

g.title: j3469146170
g.text: And in case you're thinking about making a move on any of us...

g.title: j2986281390
g.text: If I thought they knew what they were doing and had genuine feelings for the guy, I'd be thrilled. Obviously.

g.title: j3740719883
g.text: She still wants you to recover from this, though, right?

g.title: j1063375011
g.text: ... you could do worse than earn Quincy's trust. He sees a lot. Maybe you could take notes.

g.title: j4128859743
g.text: But I'd want to make sure they knew how easy it is to hurt him.

g.title: j3606521077
g.text: Oh, come on. I’ll grow wings and a tail before THAT happens.

g.title: j227430165
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j1270810227
g.text: What are those robot things that are all armour and attitude on the outside but the inside is all soft, squishy organics?

g.title: j841716901
g.text: Entrati has buggered off. If there was ever a hope of getting the old Eleanor back, the one who sang in the shower and smiled at kids in the street, that hope left with him.

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j2009304328
g.text: 솔라리스?

g.title: j4204049571
g.text: Nox?

g.title: j2200652076
g.text: Sentients?

g.title: j2278678627
g.text: Lettie needs to look in the mirror and understand she's also just a few bad days away from losing her humanity.

g.title: j2530865954
g.text: If Arthur thinks you’re still his sister, that should be good enough for Lettie, too.

g.title: j398724953
g.text: It doesn't matter. The point is, Arthur's like one.

g.title: j4021895973
g.text: Are you trying to get on my good side?

g.title: j1648266007
g.text: YOU WOULD THINK.

g.title: j2303204870
g.text: If he lets you in, for Sol's sake be gentle with him.

g.title: j172861258
g.text: I mean, yes. She does.

g.title: j4122941145
g.text: Lettie adores Arthur. He’s the big brother she never had. If Arthur wasn’t around, I’d wake up to a chloroform rag over my mouth and end up at the bottom of the river.

g.title: j1697102588
g.text: I still haven't forgiven her for what she said about letting this city burn.

g.title: j2585985155
g.text: She thinks he’s delusional, holding on to the past. But she loves the guy and she’s a good soldier, so she’ll never go against him.

g.title: j3422377479
g.text: Even Aoi was shocked. It makes you wonder who the real monsters are, doesn't it?

g.title: j1906233012
g.text: Why does she hate you so much, anyway?

g.title: j1396857966
g.text: Is it seriously just the tongue thing that freaks her out? Or is it the mind reading thing?

g.title: j1702401108
g.text: It’s complicated. There’s more than one reason.

g.title: j1069164048
g.text: She’s told me to her face that I’m not to go poking around in her head. If I didn’t agree, she’d leave the Hex and take her chances on her own. Insane stuff.

g.title: j1576457380
g.text: So part of it is just that she’s scared I’m going to read her teenage diary, as it were. I’ll peer at her most embarrassing secrets and laugh my arse off and she’ll be humiliated forever.

g.title: j1636687795
g.text: The truth is, I’m just not that curious. Whatever sick little secret she’s hiding from me, it’s safe.

g.title: j2421705015
g.text: Did you two ever have a... more romantic history together?

g.title: j1114610199
g.text: Do you think maybe she LIKES you?

g.title: j4228683458
g.text: Do you think I'd kiss and tell?

g.title: j4193918584
g.text: It’s crossed my mind.

g.title: j3183317094
g.text: No. No we didn't.

g.title: j1861435843
g.text: I’d have been up for it, I think. Nothing wrong with a snog and a grope between friends, especially if Arthur had to give us an awkward speech at briefing about how we mustn’t let our feelings get in the way of doing our job.

g.title: j1163133039
g.text: Which is just as well, because can you imagine how awkward things would be between us now?

g.title: j254966346
g.text: It blows off steam, it’s good for morale, and it’s cheap.

g.title: j2563943279
g.text: I mean... I wouldn't have said no. It just never came up.

g.title: j2004644918
g.text: But whatever Ms Garcia is hiding is something people could use to hurt her. So I’m a threat, because I might see it in her head.

g.title: j1552869110
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j2229607338
g.text: Wait, weren’t Arthur and Aoi an item?

g.title: j2414309551
g.text: So if you're attracted to her, then go for it! I'll cheer from the sidelines! Lua knows Lettie could use some happiness in her bleak, loveless life.

g.title: j2016589461
g.text: Why? You got designs on my brother? Or on Aoi?

g.title: j3029106174
g.text: Well. Um. Actually...

g.title: j2549904643
g.text: Uh... no... I have designs on *you* actually...

g.title: j2820303875
g.text: No. LOL. They're not my type, sorry. Too "heroic."

g.title: j3761573847
g.text: Oh! Oh! DO tell...

g.title: j1735567287
g.text: Interesting.

g.title: j811215380
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1085716839
g.text: 아서.

g.title: j2133905597
g.text: 아오이.

g.title: j2990585500
g.text: Sorry, that's probably not the response you were hoping for, is it?

g.title: j2103239099
g.text: 하하하

g.title: j4168544017
g.text: I KNEW IT.

g.title: j4158833008
g.text: I don't blame you one bit.

g.title: j2703932027
g.text: Well.

g.title: j2418250068
g.text: Rugged, dashing Arthur? Pure, kindhearted Aoi? Neither one of them floats your boat?

g.title: j3531797064
g.text: I don't have the heart to tell you what you're letting yourself in for. You can walk that road all by yourself.

g.title: j2358726525
g.text: I know she seems too pure to be real, but believe me, she's a soldier like the rest of us.

g.title: j2735775302
g.text: We'll see.

g.title: j1962295987
g.text: I am intrigued.

g.title: j1029407880
g.text: Just so we're clear: baiting Arthur is MY prerogative. And if you're ever cruel to him on purpose, I will murder you. One more thing...

g.title: j1626318012
g.text: Get to know the REAL Aoi, not whatever image you have in your head of her, and you'll be okay. Also...

g.title: j1924040592
g.text: We shall talk of this another time, she said, wrapping her crimson cape around her face and stalking away...

g.title: j3186352587
g.text: Arthur and Aoi’s relationship was one of the first casualties of this conflict. Neither one of them is over it. It’s a bit of an open wound, so be careful.

g.title: j366792849
g.text: Why did they break up?

g.title: j106840991
g.text: I couldn't possibly see them working out.

g.title: j4195359585
g.text: Why are you asking?

g.title: j2236923444
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j34651203
g.text: Never any harm in some harmless gossip.

g.title: j2829438952
g.text: It’d help to know, so I don’t rub salt in any open wounds.

g.title: j3138891787
g.text: Well, you're not alone.

g.title: j1904317256
g.text: Hmm. I don't agree.

g.title: j3319347373
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j3433572252
g.text: But you don't go up to grieving people and say 'I told you so'. You rally round. I did my best to comfort Arthur, and Lettie tried to patch up Aoi's broken heart.

g.title: j3826783582
g.text: Aoi's my friend. And however much of a prat Arthur may be, he's still my brother.

g.title: j2510827731
g.text: Okay. I don’t know what THEY would tell you, but from where I’m sitting, they were just pulling in different directions.

g.title: j3231853421
g.text: Tread lightly. That's all I'm saying.

g.title: j1007615915
g.text: I'm not sure I should be confiding anything in you.

g.title: j3488413506
g.text: They’re both romantics, just different kinds. Arthur wants the cottage with the roses around the door. He claims he doesn’t, but he does.

g.title: j3923290889
g.text: Gods, he even used to talk about taking over a pub sometime. I can just see him with his little crowd of regulars, pulling pints, making Sunday roasts, full of hard-won wisdom.

g.title: j1446020923
g.text: Can you see Aoi finding a place in a dream like that? I can’t. She needs to spread her wings.
